       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. INIT-GROUP-MIXED.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-GROUP.
           05  WS-NAME      PIC X(10) VALUE 'JOHN DOE'.
           05  WS-AMOUNT    PIC 9(5) VALUE 99999.
           05  WS-PACKED    PIC S9(5)V99 COMP-3 VALUE 123.45.
           05  WS-ALPHA     PIC A(5) VALUE 'HELLO'.
           05  WS-NUM2      PIC 9(3) VALUE 777.
       01  WS-CHECK-NAME    PIC X(10).
       01  WS-CHECK-AMT     PIC 9(5).
       01  WS-CHECK-PACK    PIC S9(5)V99.
       01  WS-CHECK-ALPHA   PIC A(5).
       01  WS-CHECK-NUM2    PIC 9(3).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           INITIALIZE WS-GROUP.
           MOVE WS-NAME TO WS-CHECK-NAME.
           MOVE WS-AMOUNT TO WS-CHECK-AMT.
           MOVE WS-PACKED TO WS-CHECK-PACK.
           MOVE WS-ALPHA TO WS-CHECK-ALPHA.
           MOVE WS-NUM2 TO WS-CHECK-NUM2.
           DISPLAY WS-CHECK-NAME.
           DISPLAY WS-CHECK-AMT.
           DISPLAY WS-CHECK-NUM2.
           STOP RUN.
